{"blogid": "124668052", "writerAge": "码龄6年", "writerBlogNum": "23", "writerCollect": "32", "writerComment": "3", "writerFan": "1", "writerGrade": "2级", "writerIntegral": "259", "writerName": "Qlove95", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_124668052.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "61574", "writerRankWeekly": "125997", "writerThumb": "27", "writerVisitNum": "27059", "blog_read_count": "2386", "blog_time": "已于 2022-05-18 11:25:09 修改", "blog_title": "windows下安装nodejs", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<p id=\"main-toc\"><strong>目录</strong></p>\n<p id=\"1.nodejs%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%8F%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#1.nodejs%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%8F%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\">1.nodejs下载及安装</a></p>\n<p id=\"2.%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#2.%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\">2.环境变量及下载镜像配置</a></p>\n<p id=\"2.1.%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F-toc\" style=\"margin-left:80px;\"><a href=\"#2.1.%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F\">2.1.配置环境变量</a></p>\n<p id=\"2.2%20%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F-toc\" style=\"margin-left:80px;\"><a href=\"#2.2%20%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F\">2.2 设置下载镜像</a></p>\n<hr id=\"hr-toc\"/>\n<p></p>\n<p>        最近公司项目需要本地调试前端，前端项目使用当前流行的 Ant Design Pro Vue框架，结果发现本机还没有安装nodejs，现将nodejs安装流程分享下：</p>\n<h2 id=\"1.nodejs%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%8F%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\">1.nodejs下载及安装</h2>\n<p>官方地址：<a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/\" title=\"Node.js\">Node.js</a></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"606\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\e7038e67796046a4a04c9dd57acd7f27.png\" width=\"982\"/></p>\n<p> 选择左边官网推荐的适合大多数用户的版本，我这里是16.15.0</p>\n<p>打开下载的.msi的文件，我重新配置的安装路径是D盘目录下，其他默认下一步即可</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"376\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\1c225f829f2c4db1ab30fe111333c2ef.png\" width=\"482\"/></p>\n<p>完成后打开cmd验证一下</p>\n<p>输入</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">#查看node版本\nnode -v\n#查看npm版本\nnpm -v</code></pre>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"123\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\ba8974d865cb4103916e066e3241a40d.png\" width=\"614\"/></p>\n<p>没有问题</p>\n<h2 id=\"2.%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\">2.环境变量及下载镜像配置</h2>\n<h3 id=\"2.1.%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F\">2.1.配置环境变量</h3>\n<p>在nodejs安装路径下新建两个文件夹cache和global，用来存放缓存和全局模块（否则后期配置时会默认安装到C盘用户对应的文件夹下）</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"646\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\81d3b9d9578143b0902f7d9df0993688.png\" width=\"914\"/></p>\n<p> 然后打开cmd输入</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">#设置缓存\nnpm config set cache \"D:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\cache\"\n#设置全局模块\nnpm config set prefix \"D:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\global\"</code></pre>\n<p>然后新建系统变量 NODE_PATH</p>\n<p>变量值填 D:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\node_modules</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"259\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\d1f142d8e08e449dad1faf132cd9acea.png\" width=\"858\"/></p>\n<p> 然后调整用户变量PATH里对应的值</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"839\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\4a59f355688f427b8a230299dd882623.png\" width=\"869\"/></p>\n<p>修改对应npm的值为global全局模块的路径 D:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\global,</p>\n<p>确定。</p>\n<h3 id=\"2.2%20%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F\">2.2 设置下载镜像</h3>\n<p>官网镜像下载较慢，我们使用国内淘宝镜像</p>\n<p>打开cmd，输入</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">npm config set registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org</code></pre>\n<p id=\"3.%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95\">然后测试一下</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">npm config get registry</code></pre>\n<p>完成安装！</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"136\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\46b74439703a415a99e10f3248859852.png\" width=\"830\"/></p>\n<p>(可选)安装cnpm</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">npm install cnpm -g --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</code></pre>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n</div>", "first_tag": "Others", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 0, "php": 0, "time": "2022-05-18 11:25:09", "summary": "目录下载及安装环境变量及下载镜像配置配置环境变量设置下载镜像最近公司项目需要本地调试前端，前端项目使用当前流行的框架，结果发现本机还没有安装，现将安装流程分享下：下载及安装官方地址：选择左边官网推荐的"}